Be a part of history! Join us in organizing the 10th edition of the International Conference on Language Documentation \& Conservation.

![ICLDC 2027](/images/icldc2027.png)

## Course highlights include:

- Become part of the official Student Steering Committee for the conference (CV item)
- Join subcommittees responsible for various parts of the conference organization (tech, registration, social media, food and social, travel, etc.)
- Help to evaluate abstract submissions and assign reviewers
- Discuss issues of language documentation in the context of abstracts and scholarships and decide upon scholarship recipients
- Communicate professionally with linguists across the world

